[WOMBAT] Level [1] 50 charges (--sta, --int, --mag, --ste, ++luck)
         (cannot wield weapons)

  The wombat is an interesting individual. It is capable of digging
  vast tunnel networks linking spread out areas of the mud, and dragging
  other objects around wherever it goes, among other things.

>>-------------------------------ABILITIES-------------------------------<<

sniff <monster>  Determines the alignment of given monster.

drag <object>    Drags an object that is too heavy for you to carry.

burrow           Begins digging in the current spot to make a tunnel
                 to the burrow.

forage           (16 sp) Search for potatoes in the surrounding area.
